      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the warm cloth thing but it didnt really do much. the hearing is still totally gone in that ear, it just feels hollow and silent. i dont really want to go to the doctor right now if i can avoid it, it's a hassle. do you think it's just gonna clear up on its own if i wait a day or two? feels like it might just be inflammation or something.",
