      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just looked up otosclerosis and it says that's usually like a bone thing that happens over time, not just from a pop? also i don't have any drops at home. if i just use a little bit of olive oil or something to soften it, can i just stay home and monitor it for a few days? i'm sure it's just the pressure equalizing or something similar to when you fly on a plane.",
